'''瑞贝尔·-{zh-cn:梅兰妮;zh-hk:美蓮妮;zh-tw:梅蘭妮;}-·-{zh-hk:伊莉莎伯;zh-cn:伊丽莎白;zh-tw:伊莉莎白;}-·威尔森'''（{{lang-en|Rebel Melanie Elizabeth Wilson}}，{{bd|1980年|3月2日||}}），是一名澳大利亚演員、作家及監製。2012年演出《歌喉讚》的胖艾美而聞名。

== 早年 ==
威尔森生于[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[新南威尔士州|新南威尔士州]][[悉尼|悉尼]]市<ref name="JC">{{cite web|url=http://www.jennycraig.com.au/friendofjenny/rebelwilson/about|title=Rebel Wilson|publisher=Jenny Craig, Australia & New Zealand|accessdate=15 August 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720031826/http://www.jennycraig.com.au/friendofjenny/rebelwilson/about/|archivedate=2011年7月20日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。父母是职业训犬员，威尔森的名字来自一位在两人婚礼上唱歌的女孩<ref name=EllenShow>{{cite episode|title=Rebel Wilson on Her Family|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=astcvS4QCfQ|series=The Ellen DeGeneres Show|network=[[NBCUniversal|NBCUniversal]]|quote=I've got two sisters, Liberty and Annachi and my brother Ryot...and what's her [mother's] name? Sue.|airdate=11 November 2013|access-date=2015-05-10|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208041711/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=astcvS4QCfQ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TopTen">{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118040424?refCatId=19|title=Rebel Wilson: Oz Star Gets ''Bridesmaids'' Boost|last=Blair|first=Iain|date=26 July 2011|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=[[Reed_Business_Information|Reed Business Information]]|accessdate=15 August 2011|archive-date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108233134/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118040424?refCatId=19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MField"/>。

威尔森在[[肯泽斯特|肯泽斯特]]郊区、[[帕拉马塔|帕拉马塔]]和[[城堡山|城堡山]]长大<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.okmagazine.com.au/insider/rebel-wilsons-road-to-tinsel-town.htm|title=Rebel Wilson's road to tinsel town|date=15 April 2013|work=[[OK!|OK! Australia]]|accessdate=24 December 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224115853/http://www.okmagazine.com.au/insider/rebel-wilsons-road-to-tinsel-town.htm|archivedate=2013年12月24日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/tv--radio/bboganvilleb-dont-mock-the-moccasins/2008/06/16/1213468329184.html|title=Don't be mocking the moccasins.|date=17 June 2008|work=[[The_Age|The Age]]|accessdate=24 December 2013|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401052441/http://www.theage.com.au/news/tv--radio/bboganvilleb-dont-mock-the-moccasins/2008/06/16/1213468329184.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。为避免被取笑，她在塔拉圣公会女子学校读书时把与女王同名的中间名略去<ref name="Miller">{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad/the-qa-with-actor-rebel-wilson/story-fn6bn9st-1226199246884|title=The Q&A with actor Rebel Wilson|last=Miller|first=Megan|date=19 November 2011|work=[[Herald_Sun|Herald Sun]]|publisher=[[The_Herald_and_Weekly_Times|The Herald and Weekly Times]]|accessdate=13 August 2013|archive-date=2016-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728074722/http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad/the-qa-with-actor-rebel-wilson/story-fn6bn9st-1226199246884|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elle.com.au/pop-culture/elle-interview/2013/12/elle-interview-rebel-wilson/|title=Elle interview: Rebel Wilson|date=17 December 2013|work=[[Elle_(magazine)|Elle Australia]]|accessdate=24 December 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324035908/http://www.elle.com.au/pop-culture/elle-interview/2013/12/elle-interview-rebel-wilson/|archive-date=2015-03-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieline.com/2012/09/07/bridesmaids-bachelorette-rebel-wilson-pitch-perfect-interview|title=From Bridesmaids To Bachelorette: Why Rebel Wilson Is The Most Interesting Woman In Hollywood|publisher=Movieline.com|date=7 September 2012|first=Jen|last=Yamato|accessdate=21 August 2014|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003132403/http://movieline.com/2012/09/07/bridesmaids-bachelorette-rebel-wilson-pitch-perfect-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威尔森有三个兄弟姐妹，姐妹莉柏蒂（Liberty）和安娜琪（Annachi），哥哥萊亞特（Ryot）<ref name=EllenShow/><ref name="MField">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/lifestyle/sunday-magazine/winning-laughs-and-losing-weight/story-e6frf039-1226186071421|title=Winning Laughs and Losing Weight|last=Field|first=Melissa|date=6 November 2011|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph_(Australia)|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=News Limited|accessdate=1 January 2013|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718165558/https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/lifestyle/winning-laughs-and-losing-weight/news-story/0fc280409cfd4695b0e3697b1c2e1139?nk=5a0b4d7937a1875ab512a58e60ba1965-1595091358|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Craig">{{cite video|people=Rebel Wilson, Craig Ferguson|title=The Late Late Show with Craig Ferguson|work=[[The_Late_Late_Show_with_Craig_Ferguson|The Late Late Show with Craig Ferguson]]|publisher=[[Worldwide_Pants_Incorporated|Worldwide Pants Incorporated]]|date=3 June 2011|accessdate=15 August 2011}}</ref>。莉柏蒂與萊亞特参与了澳大利亚版《[[极速前进|极速前进]]》第一季<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.couriermail.com.au/ipad/rebel-sets-pace-for-siblings/story-fn6ck8la-1226056983991|title=Rebel sets pace for siblings|last=Shearer|first=Geoff|date=17 May 2011|work=[[The_Courier-Mail|The Courier-Mail]]|publisher=[[Queensland_Newspapers|Queensland Newspapers]]|accessdate=15 August 2011|archive-date=2012-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922143732/http://www.couriermail.com.au/ipad/rebel-sets-pace-for-siblings/story-fn6ck8la-1226056983991|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威尔森的姑婆是[[華特·迪士尼|華特·迪士尼]]的妻子{{tsl|en|Lillian Disney|莉莉安·迪士尼|莉莉安·邦茲}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/weekend/entertainment/2013/10/11/funny-girl-rebel-wilson/2965553|title=Funny girl Rebel Wilson's 'Super Fun Night' inspiration|publisher=USA Today|date=11 October 2013|first=Nancy|last=Mills|accessdate=21 August 2014|archive-date=2019-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191220172812/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/weekend/entertainment/2013/10/11/funny-girl-rebel-wilson/2965553/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

威尔森的职业首选是数学。她告诉《[[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]]》，她在高中时数学学得很好，总是很擅长用数字<ref name="PushOver">{{cite news|url=http://newsstore.fairfax.com.au/apps/viewDocument.ac?page=1&sy=age&kw=Rebel+Wilson+and+University&pb=all_ffx&dt=selectRange&dr=entire&so=relevance&sf=text&sf=headline&rc=10&rm=200&sp=nrm&clsPage=1&docID=SMH020529M6EBJ21STPN|title=A push over on stage|last=Wilson|first=Vanessa|date=29 May 2002|work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|publisher=[[Fairfax_Media|Fairfax Media]]|accessdate=15 August 2011|quote=That lead to the 22-year-old's first play, The Westie Monologues, and her springboard to life as a playwright. And actor. And producer. And theatre company director.|archive-date=2012-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608152921/http://newsstore.fairfax.com.au/apps/viewDocument.ac?page=1&sy=age&kw=Rebel+Wilson+and+University&pb=all_ffx&dt=selectRange&dr=entire&so=relevance&sf=text&sf=headline&rc=10&rm=200&sp=nrm&clsPage=1&docID=SMH020529M6EBJ21STPN|dead-url=no}}</ref>。威尔逊在[[新南威尔士大学|新南威尔士大学]]时学习法律和艺术（戏剧和表演学）<ref name="PushOver"/>。作为一位前澳大利亚[[国际扶轮|国际扶轮]]青年大使，威尔森在南非待了一年就染上[[疟疾|疟疾]]<ref name="TopTen"/><ref name="PushOver"/>。疾病的痛苦让威尔逊自己产生了赢得奥斯卡奖的幻觉，这说服她去追求演艺事业<ref name="TopTen"/>。

== 私生活 ==
2011年7月，威尔森成为澳大利亚减肥营养公司珍妮·克雷格的代言人<ref name="JC"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/entertainment/confidential/rebel-wilson-seeks-to-slim-down-for-career/story-e6frf96x-1226097108580|title=Rebel Wilson seeks to slim down for career|date=19 July 2011|work=[[Herald_Sun|Herald Sun]]|publisher=[[The_Herald_and_Weekly_Times|The Herald and Weekly Times]]|accessdate=15 August 2011}}</ref>。2012年1月，威尔逊向《[[每日电讯报_(澳洲)|每日电讯报]]》透露，自签署该计划以来自己已经瘦了22磅<ref name="StayingBig">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/why-rebel-wilson-will-be-staying-big-in-hollywood/story-e6frewyr-1226250311877|title=Why Rebel Wilson will be staying big in Hollywood|last=Wigney|first=James|author2=Halliwell, Elle |date=22 January 2012|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph_(Australia)|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[News_Limited|News Limited]]|accessdate=21 January 2012}}</ref>。

她透露，《[[完美音调|完美音调]]》的制片人禁止她在拍戏期间减肥，合約要求她保持体重<ref name="StayingBig"/>。威尔森曾经说过一旦电影合約过期，就重新开始体重达到180磅的目标<ref name="StayingBig"/>。2013年2月，威尔森证实已和珍妮·克雷格在前一年解约<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/sydney-confidential/rebel-wilson-talks-on-split-with-jenny-craig/story-e6frewz0-1226580846065|title=Rebel Wilson talks on split with Jenny Craig|last=Christie|first=Joel|date=19 February 2013|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph_(Australia)|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[News_Limited|News Limited]]|accessdate=22 February 2013|archive-date=2016-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161117044628/http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/sydney-confidential/rebel-wilson-talks-on-split-with-jenny-craig/story-e6frewz0-1226580846065|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年9月，威尔森与[[马修·卢卡斯|马修·卢卡斯]]住在[[西好莱坞_(加利福尼亚州)|西好莱坞]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a403406/bridesmaids-rebel-wilson-matt-lucas-live-together-annoy-neighbours.html|title='Bridesmaids' Rebel Wilson, Matt Lucas live together, annoy neighbours|last=Wightman|first=Catriona|date=3 September 2012|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|publisher=[[Hearst_Magazines_UK|Hearst Magazines UK]]|accessdate=17 January 2013|archive-date=2013-09-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JIMLpHep?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a403406/bridesmaids-rebel-wilson-matt-lucas-live-together-annoy-neighbours.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來與Jacob Busch交往，直至2021年3月分手。2022年6月，向外界公開她的現任女友為Romana Agruma。

